metadata.name: Blue Mona Lisa
metadata.description:
Our planet's most famous painting is known as Mona Lisa. Blue Mona Lisa is her sister from space reminding us that we are not alone in our galaxy.

Blue Mona Lisa was first created as a physical acrylic painting 77 x 53 cm (30 x 21 in), same size as her sister from earth.

The first buyer of Blue Mona Lisa will have the claiming rights to the original painting and have it home delivered for free within our planet Earth. Cross planetary deliveries are not included in price.
